{"word":"H758 - אֲרָם - ʼĂrâm - arawm' - Aram","slug":"H758","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֲרָם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼĂrâm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>arawm'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Aram"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05E8;&#x05DD; - 'a&#x0306;ra&#x0302;m</b> - <i>arawm'</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/H759\">H759</a>; the <i>highland</i>; <i>Aram</i> or Syria, and its inhabitants; also the name of a son of Shem, a grandson of Nahor, and of an Israelite: - Aram, Mesopotamia, Syria, Syrians."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7421\">H7421</a>, <a href=\"#/H760\">H760</a>, <a href=\"#/H761\">H761</a>, <a href=\"#/H762\">H762</a>, <a href=\"#/H763\">H763</a>"}]}